  "source_notes": "Contemporary American Horoscopes. In February 2005, PT checked California's records.  A Raymond H. Cochran was born on the same day in Imperial County with mother's maiden name of Melvin.  Some sources give Steve Cochran's birth date as May 25, 1917 and his birth place as Eureka which is in Humboldt County.  These sources say his real name was Robert Alexander Cochran.  A little mystery!\\n\\nSy Scholfield later notes that there is no mystery. The California Birth Index lists \"Robert A Cochran, Mother: Rose, Birth: 25 June 1917, Humboldt County.\" Wikipedia has \"May 25\" in error.\\n",
